## Implementation Strategy

### MVP First (User Story 1 Only)

1. Complete Phase 1: Setup
2. Complete Phase 2: Foundational (CRITICAL - blocks all stories)
3. Complete Phase 3: User Story 1
4. **STOP and VALIDATE**: Test add and view independently
5. Demo if ready

### Incremental Delivery

1. Complete Setup + Foundational â†’ Foundation ready
2. Add User Story 1 â†’ Test independently â†’ Demo (MVP!)
3. Add User Story 2 â†’ Test independently â†’ Demo
4. Add User Story 3 â†’ Test independently â†’ Demo
5. Add User Story 4 â†’ Test independently â†’ Demo
6. Polish â†’ Final delivery

### Parallel Team Strategy

With multiple developers:

1. Team completes Setup + Foundational together
2. Once Foundational is done:
   - Developer A: User Story 1 (Add and View)
   - Developer B: User Story 2 (Update and Complete)
   - Developer C: User Story 3 (Delete)
3. Stories complete and integrate independently

